name: Victory-Class Star Destroyer
Lore: 'Commissioned by the Old Republic at end of the Clone Wars, Rendili StarDrive''s Victory-class starship is atmosphere-capable but has a low sublight speed.',
Text: 'May add 4 pilots, 6 passengers, 1 vehicle and 3 TIEs. Has ship-docking capability. Permanent pilot provides ability of 1. Adds 1 to your total power in battles at related planet sites.',
